						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="quick-facts">
						<h3>Why Choose Hero House Cleaning?</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>‚≠ê 4.8 stars from 175+ customers</li>
							<li>üí∞ Transparent pricing - starting at $160</li>
							<li>üè† Family-owned, Knoxville-based</li>
							<li>üåø Eco-friendly cleaning products</li>
